It may be more understandable in the intention of Russian artist in the time of Soviet revolution, and the European Zero Group. Their thought in providing the clearing ground for a new and radical changes. This may be the point where we often call art as a complex practice. If we viewed this from economist or politician viewpoint, it is so clear that the ground can not be clear and we have to build whatever we want on top of its obstacles. 
