Technologies have become the battle ground for most group of power, or even academic movements which are not intended to attach any applications to their work. A simplified form of teachnology as a robotic machine is being changed from our perception, and the entity has taken the form of wireless invisible creature dissolves in the air. Therefore, we go everywhere without leaving our smartphone out of sight we also doubt whether the phone lying on our bed can hear or see us without our consent. 
